sql:
SELECT sales_rep_id, quantity_sold
FROM sales
WHERE quantity_sold > 10;

external_knowledge:
- "sowers of the seeds" metaphorically refers to the customers;
- "cords of resilience (springs)" metaphorically describes the tires with a compound description that includes "springs";
- "20-inch cycle" refers to the tires with an outside diameter of 20 inches;
- "spread more than two units on average" corresponds to an average quantity sold greater than 2;
- "the sizes of these tires" refers to the product size;
- "the prices they fetched" refers to the average total price.
